tric radio halo as a\n`normal' halo plus a southern relic, strongly supporting a previous suggestion\nbased only on inspection of radio and preliminary X-ray data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 May 2014 13:05:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
