utcomes. Although the nonlocality of $H$ might seem to stay in\nconflict with various numerics-enforced cutoffs, this potentially serious\nobstacle is kept under control and effectively tamed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 May 2014 13:54:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-26"}
