$ are still\nvery low, $\\alpha\\simeq \\alpha'<10^{-3}$, the Kelvin wave cascade is fully\ndamped, vortex lines are very smooth, $S \\simeq 2 /\\ell$ and the tangle decay\nis predominantly caused by the mutual friction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 May 2014 07:44:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 12 Jul 2014 07:46:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 29 Aug 2014 08:48:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
